{{title "Scenes"}}
<h1>Scenes</h1>

<p>The scenes archive catalogs roleplay scenes from the game.  Only completed scenes show up here.  You can filter by type of scene or by the title or participant names.</p>


<div class="alert alert-info">For scenes that are still in progress or not yet shared, see the {{#link-to 'scenes-live'}}Active Scenes{{/link-to}} list.</div>

<div class="row">
    
    <div class="col pull-right">
       {{#link-to 'search-scenes' class="btn btn-default"}}<i class="fa fa-search" aria-hidden="true"></i> Search Scenes{{/link-to}}  
       {{#if isApproved}}
        {{#link-to 'scene-create' class="btn btn-primary"}}Create Scene{{/link-to}}
        {{/if}}
    </div>
    
</div>

{{scene-list scenes=model.scenes.scenes pages=model.scenes.pages sceneTypes=model.sceneTypes filter=filter page=page filterChanged=(action "filterChanged") goToPage=(action "goToPage")}}

